---
import ApplicationLayout from '../layouts/ApplicationLayout.astro';

const title = "Stainless Steel Centrifuge | Chemical & Food Grade Applications";
const description = "Alfa Laval Stainless Steel Centrifuge for use in pharmaceutical, food, hemp, wine, and juices, etc. All stainless steel contact, food-grade centrifuges.";

const jsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "Stainless Steel Centrifuge | Chemical & Food Grade Applications",
  "description": description,
  "author": {
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Sanjay Prabhu MSME",
    "jobTitle": "Centrifuge Applications Engineer",
    "worksFor": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Dolphin Centrifuge" }
  },
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "Dolphin Centrifuge",
    "url": "https://dolphincentrifuge.com"
  }
};

const toc = [
  {
    id: "Alfa-Laval-AFPX-213-Centrifuge",
    label: "Alfa Laval AFPX 213 Centrifuge",
    subItems: [
      { id: "Alfa-Laval-AFPX-213-Applications", label: "Applications" },
      { id: "Alfa-Laval-AFPX-213-Specifications", label: "Specifications" },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: "Alfa-Laval-BRPX-313-Centrifuge",
    label: "Alfa Laval BRPX 313 Centrifuge",
    subItems: [
      { id: "Alfa-Laval-BRPX-313-Applications", label: "Applications" },
      { id: "Alfa-Laval-BRPX-313-Centrifuge-Specifications", label: "Specifications" },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: "Alfa-Laval-BRPX-309-Centrifuge",
    label: "Alfa Laval BRPX 309 Beer Centrifuge",
    subItems: [
      { id: "Alfa-Laval-BRPX-309-Centrifuge-Specifications", label: "Specifications" },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: "Alfa-Laval-AFPX-207-Centrifuge",
    label: "Alfa Laval AFPX 207 70-S Three-Phase, Disc-Stack Centrifuge",
    subItems: [
      { id: "Alfa-Laval-AFPX-207-Centrifuge-Specifications", label: "Specifications" },
    ],
  },
];

const breadcrumbs = [
  { label: "Centrifuges", href: "/centrifuges/" },
  { label: "Stainless Steel Centrifuge", href: "/stainless-steel-centrifuge/" },
];

const relatedApplications = [
  { label: "Food Grade Centrifuge", href: "/food-grade-centrifuge/" },
  { label: "Beer & Wine Centrifuge", href: "/beer-wine-centrifuge/" },
  { label: "Explosion Proof Centrifuge", href: "/explosion-proof-centrifuge/" },
  { label: "Fish Processing Centrifuge", href: "/fish-processing-centrifuge/" },
];

const relatedProducts = [
  { label: "Disc Stack Centrifuge", href: "/disc-stack-centrifuge/", description: "Self-cleaning disc stack separators" },
  { label: "Centrifuge Parts & Spares", href: "/alfa-laval-centrifuge-parts/", description: "OEM-equivalent replacement parts" },
  { label: "Sample Testing Service", href: "/industrial-centrifuge-sample-testing/", description: "Test before you buy" },
];
---

<ApplicationLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonicalUrl="https://dolphincentrifuge.com/stainless-steel-centrifuge/"
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
  heroImage="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/stainless-steel-centrifuge-hero-1440.webp"
  heroImageAlt="Alfa Laval Stainless Steel Disc Stack Centrifuge"
  category="applications"
  categoryLabel="Centrifuges"
  toc={toc}
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
  relatedApplications={relatedApplications}
  relatedProducts={relatedProducts}
>

  <!-- Intro paragraphs -->
  <p><strong>Stainless steel centrifuges are specially designed disc-stack centrifuges for separating corrosive chemicals and food products. A pass-through feature allows continuous processing through stainless-steel centrifuges. A high centrifugal force of over 7,000 g separates fine sediment down to 1 micron.</strong></p>

  <p>The Alfa Laval stainless steel centrifuges are generally of the <a href="/food-grade-centrifuge/">food-grade (sanitary)</a> design configuration. This design means that all the fluid contact parts are made of high-grade stainless steel (316L).</p>

  <!-- Intro image gallery: 2-column grid -->
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6 not-prose">
    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Hemp-CBD-Oil-Ethanol-Winterization-Centrifuge-600.webp"
        alt="Hemp CBD Oil Ethanol Winterization Centrifuge"
        class="img-cap-400 w-full"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 mt-2"><strong>Stainless Steel Hemp CBD Oil Ethanol Winterization Centrifuge</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-CRPX-207-Stainless-Steel-Kelp-Seaweed-Centrifuge-600.webp"
        alt="Alfa Laval CRPX-207 Stainless Steel Kelp Seaweed Centrifuge"
        class="img-cap-400 w-full"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 mt-2"><strong>Alfa Laval CRPX-207 Stainless Steel Kelp Seaweed Centrifuge</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p>Some centrifuges have a stainless steel sludge discharge chute as well. These machines are applicable where the separated solids are of value to the customer.</p>

  <p>For example, the precipitate is a valuable extract that must have all stainless steel contact in food flavoring extraction.</p>

  <p>These food-grade centrifuges are available in a three-phase configuration, making them suitable for fish oil, rendering, and other similar applications.</p>

  <!-- Second gallery row -->
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6 not-prose">
    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Food-Grade-Stainless-Steel-3-Phase-Disc-Centrifuge-400.webp"
        alt="Alfa Laval Food Grade Stainless Steel 3-Phase Disc Centrifuge"
        class="img-cap-400"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 mt-2"><strong>Alfa Laval Food Grade Stainless Steel 3-Phase Disc Centrifuge</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Stainless-Steel-Decanter-Centrifuge-Module-600.webp"
        alt="Alfa Laval Stainless Steel Decanter Centrifuge Module"
        class="img-cap-400 w-full"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 mt-2"><strong>Alfa Laval Stainless Steel Decanter Centrifuge Module</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Stainless-Steel-Disc-Stack-Centrifuge-600.webp"
        alt="Alfa Laval Stainless Steel Disc Stack Centrifuge"
        class="img-cap-400 w-full"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 mt-2"><strong>Alfa Laval Stainless Steel Disc Stack Centrifuge</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ── AFPX 213 ── -->
  <h2 id="Alfa-Laval-AFPX-213-Centrifuge">Alfa Laval AFPX 213 Centrifuge</h2>

  <p>The Alfa Laval AFPX 213 Centrifuge is a self-cleaning, <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">disc-stack</a>, stainless-steel centrifuge with all wetted parts made of 316L stainless steel.</p>

  <p>With a 15 HP Motor, the AFPX 213 centrifuge has a bowl RPM of 4,150 and can process vegetable juice clarification at 50 GPM.</p>

  <h3 id="Alfa-Laval-AFPX-213-Applications">Applications</h3>

  <p>The Alfa Laval AFPX 213 Clarifier centrifuge is also used for the following applications.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><a href="/beer-wine-centrifuge/">Yeast Separation from Beer</a></li>
    <li><a href="/beer-wine-centrifuge/">Wine Clarification</a></li>
    <li><a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-applications/#chemical-clarification">Corrosive Chemical Clarification</a></li>
    <li><a href="/beer-wine-centrifuge/">Fruit Juice Clarification</a></li>
    <li><a href="/food-grade-centrifuge/">Flavor Extraction</a></li>
    <li>Fish Oil, Meal Separation</li>
  </ul>

  <img
    src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Food-Grade-Centrifuge-AFPX213.webp"
    alt="Alfa Laval Food Grade Centrifuge AFPX213"
    class="img-cap-400"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 -mt-3 mb-4"><strong>Alfa Laval AFPX 213 Centrifuge with Feed Pump, Sludge Tank &amp; Filters</strong></p>

  <h3 id="Alfa-Laval-AFPX-213-Specifications">Specifications</h3>

  <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto border border-gray-100 rounded-xl">
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Model Type</td><td>Alfa Laval AFPX 213 XGD 14-60</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Maximum Capacity</td><td>100 GPM on Water</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Rated Capacity</td><td>50 GPM on Hemp Ethanol Polishing</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sludge Space</td><td>3.87 Gallons</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Bowl Speed</td><td>4,600 RPM</td></tr>
        <tr><td>G-Force</td><td>7,200 Gs</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Drive Motor</td><td>15 HP</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Voltages</td><td>230 / 460 V</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Size</td><td>5' x 7' x 7' (H)</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ── BRPX 313 ── -->
  <h2 id="Alfa-Laval-BRPX-313-Centrifuge">Alfa Laval BRPX 313 Centrifuge</h2>

  <p>The Alfa Laval BRPX 313 Centrifuge is a disc-stack, stainless-steel centrifuge with all wetted parts made of 316L stainless steel.</p>

  <p>With a 15 HP C1D2 Motor, the BRPX 313 centrifuge has a bowl <strong>RPM of 5,100</strong> and can process hemp <strong>ethanol clarification at 50 GPM</strong>. The control system is also suitable for Class 1 Div 2 hazardous area applications like Hemp CBD OIl Ethanol polishing.</p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6 not-prose">
    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Ethanol-Extraction-Centrifuge-600.webp"
        alt="Hemp Extraction Centrifuge"
        class="img-cap-400 w-full"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 mt-2"><strong>Hemp Extraction Centrifuge - C1D2 Hazardous Area Certified</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img
        src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Disc-Stack-Centrifuge-Stainless-Steel-Explosion-Proof.webp"
        alt="Alfa Laval Disc Stack Centrifuge Stainless Steel Explosion Proof"
        class="img-cap-400 w-full"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 mt-2"><strong>Alfa Laval Disc Stack Centrifuge Stainless Steel Explosion Proof</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 id="Alfa-Laval-BRPX-313-Applications">Applications</h3>

  <p>The 3-phase version of the BRPX-313 centrifuge has multiple liquid/liquid/solid separation applications in the food industry. Some of these applications are:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-applications/#water-based-hemp-cbd-oil">CBD Oil from Hemp Water</a></li>
    <li><a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-applications/#fish-oil-processing">Fish Oil Separation from Stick-water</a></li>
    <li><a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-applications/#pork-fat">Pork Fat (Lard) Separation from Water</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h3 id="Alfa-Laval-BRPX-313-Centrifuge-Specifications">Specifications</h3>

  <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto border border-gray-100 rounded-xl">
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Model Type</td><td>Alfa Laval BRPX 313 SGT 24-60</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Rated Capacity</td><td>50 GPM on CBD Ethanol Clarification</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sludge Space</td><td>3.87 Gallons</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Motor HP</td><td>15 HP</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Voltages</td><td>230 / 460 V</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ── BRPX 309 ── -->
  <h2 id="Alfa-Laval-BRPX-309-Centrifuge">Alfa Laval BRPX 309 Beer Centrifuge</h2>

  <p>The Alfa Laval BRPX 309 Centrifuge is a beer-clarifying centrifuge made of stainless steel and designed for the clarification of <a href="/beer-wine-centrifuge/">Beer, Wine, Cider</a>, and other beverages.</p>

  <p>With a 10 HP Motor, the BRPX 309 centrifuge has a bowl <strong>RPM of 7,100</strong> and can process <strong>30 GPM of Beer</strong> for yeast separation.</p>

  <img
    src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-BRPX309-Stainless-Steel-Wine-Centrifuge.webp"
    alt="Alfa Laval BRPX309 Stainless Steel Wine Centrifuge"
    class="img-cap-400"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 -mt-3 mb-4"><strong>Alfa Laval BRPX 309 SGT Centrifuge for Beer, Wine, Cider Clarification</strong></p>

  <h3 id="Alfa-Laval-BRPX-309-Centrifuge-Specifications">Specifications</h3>

  <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto border border-gray-100 rounded-xl">
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Model Type</td><td>Alfa Laval BRPX 309 SGT 24-60</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Rated Capacity</td><td>30 GPM on Beer, Wine, and Cider Clarification</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sludge Space</td><td>1.35 Gallons</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Motor HP:</td><td>10 HP</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Voltages:</td><td>230 / 460 V</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ── AFPX 207 ── -->
  <h2 id="Alfa-Laval-AFPX-207-Centrifuge">Alfa Laval AFPX 207 70-S Three-Phase, Disc-Stack Centrifuge</h2>

  <p>The Alfa Laval AFPX 207 Stainless-Steel contact centrifuge is a self-cleaning disc-stack centrifuge designed for the three-phase separation of animal fat (AF), fish oil, clarified butter, fish-stickwater, edible oils, and others.</p>

  <p>With a 10 HP Motor, the AFPX 207 centrifuge has a bowl RPM of 6,400 and can process 20 GPM of animal fat at 180 F.</p>

  <img
    src="/images/stainless-steel-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-AFPX207-Food-Grade-Centrifuge.webp"
    alt="Alfa Laval AFPX207 Food Grade Centrifuge"
    class="img-cap-400"
    loading="lazy"
  />
  <p class="text-sm text-center text-gray-500 -mt-3 mb-4"><strong>Alfa Laval AFPX-207 Food Grade Centrifuge</strong></p>

  <h3 id="Alfa-Laval-AFPX-207-Centrifuge-Specifications">Specifications</h3>

  <div class="not-prose overflow-x-auto border border-gray-100 rounded-xl">
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Model Type</td><td>Alfa Laval AFPX 207 70S</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Rated Capacity</td><td>20 GPM on Animal Fat Rendering @ 180 F</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sludge Space</td><td>1.12 Gallons</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Motor HP:</td><td>10 HP</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Voltages:</td><td>230 / 460 V</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

</ApplicationLayout>
